{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, careful selection of input features is crucial within the XpertAI framework.",
    "Enhancing the performance and efficiency of the RAG model is an ongoing topic of investigation that is beyond the scope of our work.",
    "However, we anticipate that improvements in existing tools and methodologies will enhance XpertAI's overall performance.",
    "For example, better-performing retrievers and LLMs will undoubtedly improve XpertAI's capabilities.",
    "The current version of XpertAI serves as a proof of concept that XAI integrated with LLMs can be a proxy for hypothesis generation in Chemistry."
  ]
}